## Methodology

This report was generated by analyzing {{ report.span_count }} LLM operation spans against {{ report.requirement_results | length }} regulatory requirements. Each requirement maps to specific trace data fields. Coverage is calculated as the percentage of spans containing the required field data.

- **Satisfied** (>= 95% coverage): All required data is present
- **Partial** (25-94% coverage): Some data is missing
- **Missing** (< 25% coverage): Critical data not being logged
